<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hark" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hark,</orth> hear, listen, an imperative used to engage attention either to a noise or to what a person is saying: <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.404" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 404</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.262.18" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 262</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 4.2.72" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 2, 72</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 24</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 4, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.164" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 164</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>h. you, the king is coming,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.90" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 90</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>h., h.!</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.382" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 382</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.382" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 382</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. IV, 2, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.184" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. V, 184</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.2.39" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 2, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.8.51" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 8, 51</bibl> etc. <cit><quote>h. what thou else shalt do me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.495" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 495</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>h., I will tell you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.218" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 218</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>h. how I'll bribe you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 2.2.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 2, 145</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.346.145" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 346</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 3.163" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 163</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.2.305" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 2, 305</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.212" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 212</bibl>. <cit><quote>h., h., you Gods!</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 4.6.155" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 6, 155</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>h. further,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 4.9.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 9, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>there, Tyrant, there, h., h.!</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.258" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 258</bibl></cit> (a cry to set on dogs). <cit><quote>h. in thine ear,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.2.318" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. I, 2, 318</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.2.76" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 2, 76</bibl>. <emph>h. you hither,</emph> in the same sense: <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 4, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.165" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 165</bibl>. <cit><quote>h., contrymen!</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.5.27" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 5, 27</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>h. thee,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.127" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. III, 1, 127</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. jc 5.5.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. V, 5, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.192" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 192</bibl>. <cit><quote>h. ye,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.4.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 4, 29</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.4.37" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 4, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.55" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 99</bibl>. <cit><quote>h. you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.153" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 153</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.1.259" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 1, 259</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.146" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 146</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.175" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 175</bibl> etc.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>